Inhloso yalezi zinhlelo ezenziwe nguMnyango weMfundo eyisiSekelo neSABC, ukusiza behlise umthwalo kubafundi nothisha njengoba kungafundwa. Okhulumela umnyango uMnuz Elijah Mhlanga, uthe izinhlelo zizosiza ekubuyiseni isikhathi esilahlekile ngenxa yokuvalwa kwezwe okwamenyezelwa nguMengameli Cyril Ramaphosa. Uthe izinhlelo zizosakazwa eziteshini zakwaSABC zethelevishini nasemisakazweni ezingu-13. “Lezi zinhlelo zizosiza abenza uGrade 10, 11 no-matric ne-Early Childhood Development (ECD). Ezinye zezifundo ezizofundiswa kubalwa iMaths, Physical Science, English, Life Science ne-Accounting. Ngaphansi kwe-ECD kuzofundiswa izilimi zesintu ezehlukene.” UMhlanga uthe lo mkhankaso uzosiza abafundi njengoba bezobhala izivivinyo zikaJuni. “Sinxusa ukuthi basebenzise lezi zinhlelo ukuze bangasaleli emuva emsebenzini wabo baphinde balungiselele nezivivinyo. Enkundleni iYouTube kuzoba nohlelo lokufundisa abafundi. “Siyalwamukela usizo lweSABC ngalesi sikhathi ukuze kusizakale abafundi,” kusho uMhlanga. Izinhlelo zethelevishini zimi kanje: SABC 1: Msombuluko kuya ngeSonto:5 - 6 SABC 2: Msombuluko kuya ngoLwesihlanu:9.30 -11 SABC 3: Msombuluko kuya kuLwesihlanu:6 - 7 Emisakazweni zimi kanje: Umhlobo Wenene FM 2.30 - 3 Thobela FM 5 - 6 Phalaphala FM 1.30 - 2 Munghana Lonene FM 2.30 - 3 Ukhozi FM 9 - 10 ebusuku Lesedi FM 4.15 - 4.45 Ligwalagwala FM 9.10 - 9.40 Motsweding FM 7 - 7.30 ebusuku Ikwekwezi FM 10:30 - 11:00 Radio Sonder Grense 7.30 - 8 ebusuku Tru FM 9 - 11 X-K FM 9.30 - 10 Radio 2000 11.30 - 12 Izinhlelo ziyatholakala nakwi-website yomnyango. 